article.headline: Alabama State 72, Miss. Valley St. 58
article.story: ITTA BENA, Miss. (AP) -- Solomon Forbes scored 27 points and Attarius Norwood had 18 as Mississippi Valley State defeated Alabama State 72-58 on Saturday night. Hosea Butler added 13 points and Willie Neal grabbed 12 rebounds for the Delta Devils (14-4, 8-2 Southwestern Athletic Conference). Alabama State (6-13, 4-6) was led by Rafeal Campbell, who scored 17 points and pulled in nine rebounds. Alabama State shot 19-for-44 (43.2 percent) from the floor, but the Hornets turned the ball over 17 times. The Delta Devils scored 27 points off turnovers. Mississippi Valley State shot 21-for-57 (36.8 percent). Alabama State outrebounded the Delta Devils 39-38. The Hornets led at the half 35-33.
